urls.title: peskynewt
urls.description: My flikr account is a jumble of photos capturing the wonders of nature in all its forms . I live in the Eden valley of Cumbria and many of the photographs show what's here. Some images are unlikely to meet camera club photography standards, but I enjoy what I do in the hope of capturing the moment. I take a camera on every underwater adventure or walk in the woods, so please share my travels . I donate photos free to charities that promote environmental education and protection. I am a professional environmentalist 5 days a week and at the weekends, I study and record underwater habitat and species whenever I can. I get great pleasure in learning about our marine environment currently using: Olympus OMD E5 and nauticam housing - flat and dome ports Sony A7 Rii and Sony A7II in aquatica housing - flat port and dome port compact canon G7x Mk2 and sony RX100 in Fantasea/nauticam housing Lighting strobes- sea & sea D1 & D2, Inon s2000 optical firing, plus spotting light and 2000L ring flas
